<paragraph id="IAS41_38" base="SL33631" principles="no"><paranum>38</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 41"/><data name="paranum" value="38"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS41_P0193">This Standard requires a different treatment from <xref id="IAS41_X0148" base="F391407" href="../IAS20.ditamap">IAS 20</xref>, if a <xref base="SL143247" href="IAS41_8.dita#IAS41_8/IAS41_P0151">government grant<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0150"/></ph></xref> relates to a <xref base="SL143220" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0108">biological asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0021"/></ph></xref> measured at its <xref base="SL143246" href="IAS41_8.dita#IAS41_8/IAS41_P0150">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> less <xref base="F6127376" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0110">costs to sell<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0059"/></ph></xref> or a government grant requires an entity not to engage in specified <xref base="SL143218" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0104">agricultural activity<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0010"/></ph></xref>. <xref id="IAS41_X0149" base="F391408" href="../IAS20.ditamap">IAS 20</xref> is applied only to a government grant related to a biological asset measured at its cost less any accumulated depreciation and any accumulated impairment losses.</p></body></paragraph>